deck: An American actor, set to play the the big bad of Avengers 3: Thanos.
description:
Comic Related Movie Roles

Jonah Hex

In 2010, Brolin portrayed the title character in the live-action Jonah Hex movie.

Dwight McCarthy

In 2014, Josh Brolin played Dwight McCarthy in the Robert Rodriguez & Frank Miller-directed prequel/sequel to Sin City, Sin City: A Dame to Kill For.

Thanos

Brolin provides the voice for Thanos in 2014's Guardians of the Galaxy. He reprised the role in Avengers: Age of Ultron, and will do so again in the 2-part Avengers: Infinity War movie.
name: Josh Brolin

description:
Kurt has been creating Comic Books since 1992. He first entered the industry through a portfolio review with Louis Small Jr. He then started to work for publishers such as Brainstorm and Dark Fantasy.

I the late 90's he made his way into online animation, producing such features as Lucid and Moebius' Arzach.

In 2015, Kurt returned to publishing Comic Books. He put together a collection of all 3 of the original Crom the Barbarian Comic book stories from the 1950's. He also wrote and drew 3 new stories for the character.
name: Kurt Brugel
